1. Use command npm init -y
its create package.json

2. Create index.js file

3. Write "start" script with "node index.js"

4. change type to "module", we'll use es 6 syntax

5. install express, by using command npm i express 

6. inside index.js create express structure, 
build apis and run it on port 8000.

7. start server by using command npm start 

8. use thunder client to call apis to get response


